OL,3,CCharities warn of record child poverty
OL,4,Cif two-child benefit cap not scrapped
OL,6,FUK charities have warned Sir Keir
OL,7,FStarmer that scrapping the two-child
OL,8,Fbenefit limit is the most cost-
OL,9,Feffective way to reduce child poverty.
OL,11,FIn a letter to the prime minister,
OL,12,Fgroups including Barnardo's, Save the
OL,13,FChildren UK and Citizens Advice said
OL,14,Ffailure to scrap the limit could put
OL,15,Fchild poverty at its highest level
OL,16,Fsince records began by the end of this
OL,17,Fparliament.
