OL,3,CCharities warn of record child poverty
OL,4,Cif two-child benefit cap not scrapped
OL,6,FAs part of its new child poverty plan,
OL,7,Fcharities are increasing pressure on
OL,8,Fthe government to ditch the benefit
OL,9,Frestrictions.
OL,11,FIt is expected to be published in
OL,12,Fspring but the End Child Poverty
OL,13,FCoalition has said it believes the
OL,14,Fdocument might not come until June.
OL,16,FThe letter urges Starmer to "direct
OL,17,Fthe full weight of your government
OL,18,Finto reducing child poverty with
OL,19,Furgency".
