OL,3,CCharities warn of record child poverty
OL,4,Cif two-child benefit cap not scrapped
OL,6,FIt reads: "Scrapping the two-child
OL,7,Flimit is by far the most cost-
OL,8,Feffective way to reduce child poverty.
OL,10,F"It would lift 350,000 children out of
OL,11,Fpoverty overnight and result in
OL,12,F700,000 children living in less deep
OL,13,Fpoverty.
