OL,3,CCharities warn of record child poverty
OL,4,Cif two-child benefit cap not scrapped
OL,6,FThe Child Poverty Action Group, which
OL,7,Fsigned the letter, estimates that the
OL,8,Fnumber of children in poverty will
OL,9,Fjump from 4.5 million currently, to
OL,10,F4.8 million by 2029 unless urgent
OL,11,Faction is taken.
OL,13,FThe two-child limit was first
OL,14,Fannounced in 2015 by the Conservatives
OL,15,Fand came into effect on April 6 2017.
OL,17,FIt restricts child tax credit and
OL,18,Funiversal credit (UC) to the first two
OL,19,Fchildren in most households.
